# game/Scenes/Mari/MariConversations/marip1.rpy:16
translate chinese marip1_ec4a3669:

    # fr "This is a hard story for me to tell. Are you sure you want to hear about it?"
    fr "这对我来说是个很难说出口的故事。你确定想听吗？"

# game/Scenes/Mari/MariConversations/marip1.rpy:19
translate chinese marip1_124cbb0b:

    # fr "I trust you and I like you. I want you to know about it."
    fr "我相信你，我也喜欢你。我想让你知道这件事。"

# game/Scenes/Mari/MariConversations/marip1.rpy:21
translate chinese marip1_c9426e7f:

    # fr "Okay. I trust you and I want you to know about it."
    fr "好的。我相信你，我也希望你知道这件事。"

# game/Scenes/Mari/MariConversations/marip1.rpy:25
translate chinese marip1_d41d8cd9:

    # voice 'voices/mari_yeah.mp3'
    voice 'voices/mari_yeah.mp3'

# game/Scenes/Mari/MariConversations/marip1.rpy:26
translate chinese marip1_e1a717b7:

    # fr "Yeah, let's not talk about sad stuff today."
    fr "是啊，今天别聊伤心事了。"

# game/Scenes/Mari/MariConversations/marip1.rpy:27
translate chinese marip1_a5b1d94c:

    # fr "Maybe some other time."
    fr "也许改天再说吧。"

# game/Scenes/Mari/MariConversations/marip1.rpy:30
translate chinese marip1_dc5e9084:

    # fr "So I'll tell you what happened."
    fr "那我就告诉你当时发生了什么。"

# game/Scenes/Mari/MariConversations/marip1.rpy:31
translate chinese marip1_89daecb4:

    # fr "We were all packed into my dad's SUV, driving to a restaurant in Whiterock."
    fr "我们挤在我爸的SUV里，正开车去怀特洛克的一家餐厅。"

# game/Scenes/Mari/MariConversations/marip1.rpy:32
translate chinese marip1_4ecefbf2:

    # fr "This was nearly 4 years ago. I was 18."
    fr "那是将近4年前的事了。我当时18岁。"

# game/Scenes/Mari/MariConversations/marip1.rpy:33
translate chinese marip1_f52ca67a:

    # fr "My dad was driving, mom was in the passenger seat, and I was sitting in the back with my grandmother and my Aunt Susan."
    fr "我爸在开车，妈妈坐在副驾驶座，我坐在后排，和我奶奶还有苏珊阿姨在一起。"

# game/Scenes/Mari/MariConversations/marip1.rpy:35
translate chinese marip1_073ae7ca:

    # fr "When our car was on the bridge that leads into Whiterock, a semi-truck coming in the other direction veered over into our lane and hit us head-on."
    fr "当我们的车开上通往怀特洛克的那座桥时，一辆迎面驶来的半挂卡车突然偏离车道，与我们迎面相撞。"

# game/Scenes/Mari/MariConversations/marip1.rpy:36
translate chinese marip1_9a1c473f:

    # fr "I woke up nearly a month later and I couldn't remember anything."
    fr "我醒来时已过去近一个月，却什么都不记得了。"

# game/Scenes/Mari/MariConversations/marip1.rpy:37
translate chinese marip1_68df3d2e:

    # fr "The doctor told me that they had all been killed in the accident. The truck driver had fallen asleep at the wheel. He was dead too."
    fr "医生告诉我，他们在事故中全都遇难了。卡车司机当时在驾驶时睡着了。他也死了。"

# game/Scenes/Mari/MariConversations/marip1.rpy:38
translate chinese marip1_944ca833:

    # fr "I was the only survivor."
    fr "我是唯一的幸存者。"

# game/Scenes/Mari/MariConversations/marip1.rpy:39
translate chinese marip1_2dffe0f5:

    # fr "My whole life was in that car, wiped away in an instant."
    fr "我的一生都在那辆车里，转瞬即逝。"

# game/Scenes/Mari/MariConversations/marip1.rpy:40
translate chinese marip1_7c8d475f:

    # fr "Now all that I have left is my farm and my animals."
    fr "如今我仅剩的只有农场和我的动物们。"

# game/Scenes/Mari/MariConversations/marip1.rpy:41
translate chinese marip1_36223d79:

    # fr "That's why they mean so much to me, and also why I've never learned to drive. I'm pretty scared of cars."
    fr "这就是它们对我如此重要的原因，也是我从未学会开车的原因。我真的很怕车。"

# game/Scenes/Mari/MariConversations/marip1.rpy:44
translate chinese marip1_61b06a2b:

    # fr "Yeah. Sorry to bring down the date."
    fr "是啊。抱歉让气氛变得沉重。"

# game/Scenes/Mari/MariConversations/marip1.rpy:45
translate chinese marip1_7e2a8815:

    # pc "It's okay, I wanted to know. Thank you for telling me."
    pc "没关系，我本就想知道。谢谢你告诉我。"

# game/Scenes/Mari/MariConversations/marip1.rpy:46
translate chinese marip1_b8c78b04:

    # fr "You're welcome."
    fr "不客气。"

# game/Scenes/Mari/MariConversations/marip1.rpy:51
translate chinese marip1_90a640e6:

    # fr "Thank you."
    fr "谢谢。"

# game/Scenes/Mari/MariConversations/marip1.rpy:52
translate chinese marip1_f648d2ef:

    # "I hold her like that for a bit, while she cries the rest of her tears out."
    "我就这样抱着她一会儿，任她把剩下的眼泪都哭干。"

# game/Scenes/Mari/MariConversations/marip1.rpy:53
translate chinese marip1_ec648553:

    # "Then she pulls away."
    "然后她挣脱开来。"

# game/Scenes/Mari/MariConversations/marip1.rpy:58
translate chinese marip1_42ad97de:

    # fr "Yeah, no kidding."
    fr "是啊，真的。"

# game/Scenes/Mari/MariConversations/marip1.rpy:59
translate chinese marip1_236f25d9:

    # fr "Now I'm going to wipe my eyes and we're going to only talk about happy stuff the rest of the time. Deal?"
    fr "我现在去擦擦眼泪，剩下的时间我们只聊开心的事。行吗？"

# game/Scenes/Mari/MariConversations/marip1.rpy:60
translate chinese marip1_8ef8e0e9:

    # pc "Deal."
    pc "行。"

